approvedrevs-revision-nav:
{{Optional}}
An expansion of the core MediaWiki message {{msg-mw|Revision-nav}}.

Parameters:
* $1 - prev diff. link text is {{msg-mw|Diff}}
* $2 - prev link. link text is {{msg-mw|Previousrevision}}
* $3 - approved link. link text is {{msg-mw|Approvedrevs-approvedrevision}}
* $4 - approved diff. link text is {{msg-mw|Diff}}
* $5 - link. link text is {{msg-mw|Currentrevisionlink}}
* $6 - cur diff. link text is {{msg-mw|Diff}}
* $7 - next link. link text is {{msg-mw|Nextrevision}}
* $8 - next diff. link text is {{msg-mw|Diff}}
